Name: Average time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time between Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION and Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time between Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER and Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time between Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER and Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time for Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR grouped by case:Amount
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' and the end of case grouped by the last value of case:Amount

Name: Total time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR across all process variants that include both activities
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time from the last rejection (e.g., Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR or Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION) to Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: the average of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' or `ACTIVITY` == 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' or `ACTIVITY` == 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' or `ACTIVITY` == 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' or `ACTIVITY` == 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' or `ACTIVITY` == 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and the last time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average duration of Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR when preceded directly by Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION versus when preceded by Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Elapsed time between Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR and Request Payment, to assess downstream impact of delays in final approval
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Average time it takes Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR to be performed after the first submission in cases involving multiple resubmissions
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average waiting time to Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR after the case reaches the supervisors queue (i.e., after Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Minimum time between Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION and Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR in variants without intermediate rejections
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR in variants that include no rejections versus variants that include at least one rejection
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total resolution time of Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR in domestic declaration cases (inferred from absence of pre-approval steps) versus travel cost reimbursement cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
